This is a good stroller overall. But has some major flaws. The frame is extremely flexible which makes it hard to manoeuvre. If you like myself and you live in a place with snow, forget going out if there is a snowstorm or snow that hasn't been pack down or sidewalks that haven't been plowed. It is very compact and fold amazingly into my truck and is a very sleek look in comparison to other double strollers an overall is a great stroller but using it in the snow is a big No-No. Also if you are using it with a toddler in the front it becomes extremely heavy and almost impossible to lift the stroller up to go over curbs or onto the bus etc like the wheels will literally not go up a 2 inch curb without getting stuck. it's actually quite sad because overall the stroller is good if these design features would be handled.

review_title: Very good Winter cover. Unfortunately zipper is very cheap and has broken
reviews:
I waited to give my feedback on this product as I was very skeptical as to the durability of this product.

I've used this product now about a dozen times and feel that it is a fair amount of time to give a review.

I love this product because it has given me the peace of mind that my toddler will be kept warm in cold weather.
Thus far ive only used it in - 15 and it has done the trick very well.
I like that it fits well on my baby trend jogger stroller as well as on my expand evenflo stroller.

Thebonly flaw about thisbstroller is the zipper that goes around the main windownis extremely flimsy. It almost feels as though it will break when I use it.
Another con would be that its NOT ment for rain. Personally this isnt a problem foe me but could be for others. It retains water quite a bit.

Thankfully i dont need to use this window often as i dont think it would withstand content use.

Update : Feb 6 20

I've been using this stroller cover everyday since it began snowing in November and as stated on the arrival of the product the zipper is super flimsy. Today wall out in a snowstorm one of the zippers as there are two for the window broke completely off. The product is a great idea but unfortunately the very cheap zipper lowers the value of this product.
